name: TodayinMedalofHonorHistory
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Developer Terms of Use
des:
The stories of the heroes of the United States Military should never be forgotten. Whether you are a history buff, are interested in learning more about the heroism of our nation's bravest, or want to be inspired by acts of selfless sacrifice, enable this flash briefing in order to receive information about actions that resulted in presentation of the Medal of Honor. 

Citations obtained from https://thisdayinusmilhist.wordpress.com/
